data.description: Lovely well-built home has over 4000sqft & 5 spacious bedrooms with a very comfortable floor plan. First floor Is warm and intimate. Foyer leads to Formal Dining and living area. Kitchen, Living room, and office/ sunroom overlook the beautiful back deck and pine woods. Primary bedroom, plus another first floor bedroom and two full baths. Second story has a private stairway which leads to the other large bedrooms and rec space.
